Noyer Says Euro Area Needs More Integration Before Euro Bonds

-- B y   M a r k   D e e n
-- 
2011-10-16T16:59:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-16/noyer-says-euro-area-needs-more-integration-before-euro-bonds.html
Bank of France Governor Christian
Noyer said that euro area economies need to be more integrated
before they can contemplate issuing common bonds.  “Euro bonds require extremely strong integration,” he
said today on TV5 Monde.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mark Deen in Paris at 
